      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, that math seems a bit off to me. if it's 25% of 150k, shouldn't it be 37,500 but you said the 5-year period usually uses a half-year convention? can you explain how the value actually \"disappears\" from the books over that period? like, what is the logic behind how the value is stripped away year by year?",
